*ppp-2.4.4-r7 (14 Jun 2007)

  14 Jun 2007; Alin Năstac <mrness@gentoo.org> -ppp-2.4.4-r6.ebuild,
  +ppp-2.4.4-r7.ebuild:
  Correct auth-fail paragraphs of the pppd man page (#180180).

*ppp-2.4.4-r6 (09 Jun 2007)

